{"tid":1656600,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【無神的國土 你們都要信習大帝】習下令全面掃蕩 中國定調外籍傳教士「都是間諜」","createTime":"2019-10-15T16:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:12:32.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69585778cc1dd5178794013bb3952f9a4c7a8e9e","tid":1656600,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CGNJgnE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCGNJgnE.jpg&h=4550a9c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國國家主席習近平獲終身任期後，陡然加大打壓宗教力道，外媒披露，當局目前已將所有的外籍傳教士定調為「間諜」，積極進行追捕並試圖將其全數驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌今天刊文指出，中國長年對外輸出網路技術監控他國國民、派出「學生間諜」至各大西方大學，甚至還利用大量華僑做為間諜，在建築龐大「間諜系統」的同時，北京當局卻將所有的基督教外籍傳教士稱作間諜並加以排查。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，從中央到地方，中國各級政府現已將排除外籍傳教士定為主要目標之一，各地陸續傳出大批傳教士被捕並遭控間諜，有的人甚至不是神職人員，僅因其為外籍人士且具有信仰就被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，這些外籍信徒或傳教士遭抓捕並等候遣返期間，會被有關部門強迫簽署悔過切結書，5年內禁止入境中國，有的人甚至被逼得指證其他信徒或傳教士，凸顯當局手段之惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2015.11/2015.11.02/southpark/031.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2015%2FArticle%2F2015.11%2F2015.11.02%2Fsouthpark%2F031.png&h=196a20bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/asdasdsddsdsd_YOgGt_1200x0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fasdasdsddsdsd_YOgGt_1200x0.JPG&h=c6f931dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/askdjaskldjskld_VEgdZ_1200x0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Faskdjaskldjskld_VEgdZ_1200x0.JPG&h=bdcb5f5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7821e925fdcd8bc9d35247615a12cfaafe8d843","tid":1656600,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"66f447c1e5784fb2ea06e04b783d9c590205aa81","tid":1656600,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"義和團時代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求幫推 p牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4798d1e7584ed853e9a4fefbd0ebed1976ebd540","tid":1656600,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"義和團2.0"}]}